******************
* PBHS Assistant *
******************

PBHS Assistant compiles useful shortcuts that help with site setup, finding themes information, and using our sites.

| CHANGE LOG |

** 2.0.1 **
Added update URL to manifest for auto updating on Firefox.

** 2.0.0 **
Throwing backwards compatibility out the window!

Brought extension up to current browser extension standards meaning it now works in both Google Chrome and Firefox!
Removed deprecated options page in favor of the new browser agnostic standard.
Removed SEO Checkup functionality as most of those features are now a part of SEO Tools on wordpress.
Removed old template credential/login ability.
Added a polyfill for showDialog so that the DNS tool works in Firefox.
Changed styling of the browseraction popup.
Admin login will only try to login if credentials are actually set.